<ul>
<li><p>添加dependencies
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>添加dependencies </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
